OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784429266
OL,3,CJosh Kerr smashes 27-year world record
OL,4,Cfor fastest mile at London Stadium
OL,6,FGreat Britain's Josh Kerr backed up
OL,7,Fhis bravado to smash the mile world
OL,8,Frecord at the London Diamond League.
OL,10,FHaving raised eyebrows in March by
OL,11,Fannouncing his intention to wipe out
OL,12,FMoroccan Hicham El Guerrouj's 27-year-
OL,13,Fold mark, Kerr delivered a spectacular
OL,14,Fthree minutes 42.66 seconds on
OL,15,FSaturday.
OL,17,FThe Olympic 1500m silver medallist and
OL,18,F2023 world champion decked out in a
OL,19,Fcustom speed suit and spikes designed
OL,20,Fby sponsors Brooks to maximise
OL,21,Faerodynamics and improve breathability.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
