FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784429266
OL,3,CJosh Kerr smashes 27-year world record
OL,4,Cfor fastest mile at London Stadium
OL,6,FKerr, 28, proved he could practice
OL,7,Fwhat he preached by blazing to the
OL,8,Ffinish, beating Moroccan El Guerrouj's
OL,9,Frecord - untouched since 1999 - by
OL,10,Fnearly half a second in front of
OL,11,F60,000 fans at the London Stadium.
OL,13,FHe finished well ahead of American
OL,14,FYared Nuguse, who was second in
OL,15,F3:45.69, while Briton Jake Heyward
OL,16,Frounded out the podium in a personal-
OL,17,Fbest 3:46.73.
OL,19,FKerr became the seventh British
OL,20,Fathlete to claim the mile record and
OL,21,Ffirst since Steve Cram in 1985.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
