FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784429266
OL,3,CJosh Kerr smashes 27-year world record
OL,4,Cfor fastest mile at London Stadium
OL,6,FHe had lined up as the sixth-fastest
OL,7,Fman in history over the mile with a
OL,8,FBritish record personal best of
OL,9,F3:45.34.
OL,11,FKerr told BBC Sport: "If I am to leave
OL,12,Fmy mark on this sport as a British
OL,13,Flegend, following in the footsteps of
OL,14,Fthe legends behind me, I have to put
OL,15,Fin those performances.
OL,26,@sD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784429266
OL,3,CJosh Kerr smashes 27-year world record
OL,4,Cfor fastest mile at London Stadium
OL,6,F"Those performances take every single
OL,7,Fpart of you, every single part of your
OL,8,Fteam. The amount of work behind the
OL,9,Fscenes is incredible. Today it was a
OL,10,Fperformance I was able to bring out -
OL,11,FI just hoped it would be a little bit
OL,12,Ffaster!"
OL,14,FThe Edinburgh athlete branded the
OL,15,Fattempt "Project 222", a nod to the
OL,16,Fnumber of seconds it takes to run a
OL,17,F3:42.00 mile - his ambitious target.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@HO]wD@IOUwD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
