PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784429266
OL,3,CJosh Kerr smashes 27-year world record
OL,4,Cfor fastest mile at London Stadium
OL,6,FKerr's previous personal best, the
OL,7,F3:45.34 British record he set at the
OL,8,FPrefontaine Classic in 2024, was also
OL,9,F2.21 seconds slower than El Guerrouj's
OL,10,Fmark.
OL,12,FThe Scot made a similar statement of
OL,13,Fintent months before breaking Sir Mo
OL,14,FFarah's indoor two-mile record in
OL,15,FFebruary 2024, and said he had not
OL,16,Fmissed a training session in the build-
OL,17,Fup to this attempt.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
