PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784429266
OL,3,CJosh Kerr smashes 27-year world record
OL,4,Cfor fastest mile at London Stadium
OL,6,FOn Friday evening, Kerr revealed via
OL,7,Fhis YouTube channel that he had run a
OL,8,Fhand-timed 1200m split of 2:42.45 at
OL,9,F5,335 feet of elevation in Albuquerque
OL,10,Fin a recent training session, though
OL,11,Fit was with a flying start.
OL,13,FIt was nevertheless 3.989 seconds
OL,14,Ffaster than El Guerrouj at the same
OL,15,Fpoint in his world record race, and
OL,16,F2.3secs faster than the Moroccan's
OL,17,Fsplit ` believed to have been the
OL,18,Ffastest recorded at 1200m ` when he
OL,19,Fattempted to break his own record in
OL,20,F2002.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
