PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784429266
OL,3,CJosh Kerr smashes 27-year world record
OL,4,Cfor fastest mile at London Stadium
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FYesterday, ahead of the attempt Kerr
OL,12,Fsaid he was "not scared of failing",
OL,13,Fadding: "There's different breeds of
OL,14,Fpeople.
OL,16,F"I'm on the attack at all times and
OL,17,FI'm bold with what I talk about, but
OL,18,Fwhen the figures and the stats behind
OL,19,Fme are backing up my claims, I don't
OL,20,Fsee why I can't go out there and do
OL,21,Fwhat my job is.
OL,26,@tD@MOUtD@cO]uD@IOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784429266
OL,3,CJosh Kerr smashes 27-year world record
OL,4,Cfor fastest mile at London Stadium
OL,6,F"And I think it's important to tell
OL,7,Fpeople what your goals are. I think it
OL,8,Fkeeps you honest.
OL,10,F"It keeps everyone honest within track
OL,11,Fand field and hopefully I can bring a
OL,12,Fcouple more eyeballs on it as well.
OL,14,F"I'm not fearing that in any way. I'm
OL,15,Fjust going out there and doing what
OL,16,FI've said that I'm capable of doing.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
