OL,3,CJosh Kerr smashes 27-year world record
OL,4,Cfor fastest mile at London Stadium
OL,6,F"I'm trying to do something that no
OL,7,Fone's ever done. There's definitely a
OL,8,Frisk of failure, but it's not
OL,9,Fsomething that's on my mind
OL,10,Fparticularly often."
